title: TV Shows Re-castings
subtitle: These actors were recast midway during the shows running time.
description: TV shows sometimes make recastings on certain roles and it could be for a variety of reasons. Inspired by the possible recasting of Henry Cavill in The Witcher, I scraped data from news articles and Wikipedia to get the names and seasons that actors/actresses were replaced, as well as their respective networks.
